                        <title_54465636
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2025-05-02T03:17:34.980-04:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-08-08T03:29:15.225-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="nandivx5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Patient group disclosures"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_1871744665
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2025-05-02T03:18:09.537-04:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-05-05T10:31:24.484-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            langAttribute="none"
                            text="&lt;p>AbbVie collaborates and co-creates with the groups working with and representing patients. The grants we provide patient groups to support their ongoing work can be found here.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Reporting Period 1 January 2023 to 31 December 2023 can be viewed by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/dam/abbvie-com2/au/docs/AbbVie_HCO_Support_Report_2023.pdf&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255,255,255);&quot;>here&lt;/a>&lt;span>.&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Reporting Period 1 January 2024 to 31 December 2024 can be viewed by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/dam/abbvie-com2/au/docs/abbvie-pty-ltd-patient-organisation-report-2024.pdf&quot;>here&lt;/a>.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Reporting Period 1 January 2025 to 31 December 2025&amp;nbsp;can be viewed by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/dam/abbvie-com2/au/docs/abbvie-pty-ltd-2025-patient-organisation-report.pdf&quot;>here&lt;/a>.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_2028598970
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756486159]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2025-05-02T03:28:55.452-04:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-05-02T03:38:16.718-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="singarx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_9787831
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2025-05-02T03:29:06.440-04:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-08-08T03:32:16.886-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="nandivx5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Government disclosures"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_1690484945
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2025-05-02T03:30:11.248-04:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-05-05T10:32:04.403-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            langAttribute="none"
                            text="&lt;p>AbbVie engages with the Australian Government to participate, as appropriate, in ongoing discussions on the healthcare environment, including access to medicines and healthcare reform. AbbVie contributes to these by sharing global knowledge, insights, and safety and efficacy data, as appropriate, on relevant therapies. AbbVie does not provide cash donations to political parties in Australia. As part of our engagement with Government we attend and occasionally sponsor political events and roundtable discussions where public policy on the healthcare environment is discussed.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>In 2023, our expenditure in attending political events was:&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;table cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;100&quot;>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;tbody>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Labor:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$15,000&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Coalition:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$13,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Total:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$28,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;/tbody>&lt;/table>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>In 2024, our expenditure in attending political events was:&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;table cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;100&quot;>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;tbody>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Labor:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$15,000&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Coalition:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$13,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Total:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$28,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;/tbody>&lt;/table>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>In 2025, our expenditure in attending political events was:&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;table cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;100&quot;>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;tbody>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Labor:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$15,000&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Coalition:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$13,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td>Total:&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;td>$28,636&lt;/td>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/tr>&lt;/tbody>&lt;/table>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                    </container_33894100_c>
